          <h1>INTRODUCTION</h1><hr>
         </header>
          <p>
            VuePress is composed of two parts: a minimalistic static site generator with a Vue-powered theming
            system and Plugin API, and a default theme optimized for writing technical documentation. It was
            created to support the documentation needs of Vue's own sub projects. <br><br>
            
            Each page generated by VuePress has its own pre-rendered static HTML, providing great loading
            performance and is SEO-friendly. Once the page is loaded, however, Vue takes over the static content
            and turns it into a full Single-Page Application (SPA). Additional pages are fetched on demand as
            the user navigates around the site.
        </p> 
